Package: Friedman
Title: Simple Tools for Transaction Data and Association Rules
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Veronica", "Vaccaro", email = "veronicavaccaro@usf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides simple functions for importing transaction data,
    summarizing item frequencies, and generating basic association rules.
    This package is designed for students and beginners working on small
    data mining projects in R.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports:
    arules,
    arulesViz
License: CC0
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/veronicavaccaro/Friedman
